Hi David, 

We are still trying to identify any issues. It's a tricky one to pin-point as some transactions are still coming through. 

Also, some of the incomplete transactions are due to the credit card itself being declined, likely due to a lack of funds. 

Rest assured we are working on finding anything that may be causing this. We are spinning up a different solution in staging at the moment which may help to shed some light on the situation. In particular we are looking into whether the mobile view is a culprit or not. 

We will keep you updated.
